    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n      <strong>School:</strong>&nbsp;illusion&nbsp;(figment);\n    <br>\n    <strong>Level:</strong>&nbsp;Bard 6, Sorcerer 6, Wizard 6;\n    <strong>Domain:</strong>&nbsp;Creation 7;\n    \n    \n    \n    <br>\n    <strong>Components:</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (powdered jade worth 100 gp), F (a bit of fleece)<br>\n    \n      <strong>Casting Time:</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Range:</strong>&nbsp;long (400 ft. + 40 ft./level)<br>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Effect:</strong>&nbsp;Figment that cannot extend beyond a 20-ft. cube + one 10-ft. cube/level (S)<br>\n    <strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;Permanent (D)<br>\n    <strong>Power Points/Spell Points Cost:</strong>&nbsp;11<br>\n        <strong>Saving Throw:</strong>&nbsp;Will disbelief (if interacted with)\n        <br>\n        <strong>Spell Resistance:</strong>&nbsp;no<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell creates the visual illusion of an object, creature, or force, as visualized by you. The figment includes visual, auditory, olfactory, and thermal elements, and the spell is permanent. By concentrating, you can move the image within the limits of the range, but it is static while you are not concentrating. You can move the image within the limits of the size of the effect.</p>\n<p><em>Material Component: </em>A bit of fleece plus powdered jade worth 100 gp.</p>\n<p><em>Focus:</em> A bit of fleece.&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n",
